  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mimi the Cat - New Friends </i> is a sokoban-style game where you can push boxes, stack boxes, and even jump between platforms, so that the lovely little cat Mimi can have her well-deserved rest in her bed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/b813930ea65aba8234c80332e5a36f46.poster.avif?t=1767498278\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/b813930ea65aba8234c80332e5a36f46.webm?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/b813930ea65aba8234c80332e5a36f46.mp4?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay close attention to the environment! Throughout the game, you will have the opportunity to unlock a new adorable cat or continue to the next levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/efed48b44f605fa2cbf305587253e2d5.poster.avif?t=1767498278\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/efed48b44f605fa2cbf305587253e2d5.webm?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/efed48b44f605fa2cbf305587253e2d5.mp4?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose to play with the unlocked kitten instead of Mimi.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/c0247a6b2f788f86461c85544ad23aeb.poster.avif?t=1767498278\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/c0247a6b2f788f86461c85544ad23aeb.webm?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/c0247a6b2f788f86461c85544ad23aeb.mp4?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no time limit or resources to manage, so you can calmly focus on solving the challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 50 handcrafted levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A tip on how many boxes are needed. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/6d8a5cf80634e6a1f1819c30954baef1.poster.avif?t=1767498278\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/6d8a5cf80634e6a1f1819c30954baef1.webm?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/6d8a5cf80634e6a1f1819c30954baef1.mp4?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Jump between platforms, like a good cat would. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/344db5e0898008445ec5573b12cfcbc0.poster.avif?t=1767498278\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/344db5e0898008445ec5573b12cfcbc0.webm?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2454020/extras/344db5e0898008445ec5573b12cfcbc0.mp4?t=1767498278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock new kittens. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stack boxes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Minimalist interface and gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Restart level. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Catchy soundtrack. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose another kitten to play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun and sweet sokoban with relaxing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mimi, Branquinho, Nevezinho, Melzinha, Cinzendo, Negan, are here to warm your heart ♥</h2>",
